In [9]:
def lemmatize_stemming(text):
    stemmer = LancasterStemmer()
    return stemmer.stem(WordNetLemmatizer().lemmatize(text, pos='v'))
def preprocess(text):
    result = []
    for token in gensim.utils.simple_preprocess(text):
        if token not in gensim.parsing.preprocessing.STOPWORDS and len(token) > 3:
            result.append(lemmatize_stemming(token))
    return result

In [27]:
for i in range(0,10000,1000):
  for j in range(1000):
    globals()['cc'+str(int(i/1000))]=[]
    for index, score in sorted(globals()['lda_model'+str(int(i/1000))][globals()['bow_corpus'+ str(int(i/1000))][j]], key=lambda tup: -1*tup[1]):
      for ind, t in globals()['lda_model'+str(int(i/1000))].show_topics(-1):
        if (t==globals()['lda_model'+str(int(i/1000))].print_topic(index)):
          globals()['cc'+str(int(i/1000))].append(ind)
    
    globals()['ss'+str(int(i/1000))].append(globals()['cc'+str(int(i/1000))])

for i in range(0,10000,1000):
  for p in range(10):
    globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(p))]=pd.DataFrame()
  for a in range(1000):
    for b in globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))]['topic_num'][a:a+1]:
      for c in b:
      #print(c)
        c=int(c)
        if(c==0):
          
          ssdl0=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl0)
        elif(c==1):
          
          ssdl1=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl1)
        elif(c==2):
          
          ssdl2=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl2)
        elif(c==3):
          
          ssdl3=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl3)
        elif(c==4):
          
          ssdl4=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl4)
        elif(c==5):
          
          ssdl5=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl5)
        elif(c==6):
          
          ssdl6=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl6)
        elif(c==7):
          
          ssdl7=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl7)
        elif(c==8):
          
          ssdl8=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl8)
        else:
          
          ssdl9=globals()['final'+str(int(i/1000))].iloc[a:a+1,[2]]
          globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))]=globals()['app_'+str(int(i/1000))+'_topic'+str(int(c))].append(ssdl9)

  coherence_lda = coherence_model_lda.get_coherence()
  print('\nCoherence Score {}: {} '.format(int(i/1000), coherence_lda))

In [42]:
import warnings
In [43]:
def compute_lda_coherence_values(bow_corpus,dictionary,P,stop, start, step):
    
    coherence_values = []
    model_list = []
    
    num_topics=10
    for num_topics in range(start, stop, step):
        warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", category=DeprecationWarning)
        model = gensim.models.LdaMulticore(bow_corpus, num_topics=num_topics, id2word=dictionary,passes=2,workers=2)
        model_list.append(model)
        
        coherencemodel = CoherenceModel(model=model, texts=P, dictionary=dictionary, coherence='c_v')
        coherence_values.append(coherencemodel.get_coherence())
    print(coherence_values)
    return model_list, coherence_values
In [44]:
def plot_lda_graph(bow_corpus,dictionary,P,start, stop, step):
    
    model_list, coherence_values = compute_lda_coherence_values(bow_corpus,dictionary,P,stop, start, step)
    # Show graph
    x = range(start, stop, step)
    plt.plot(x, coherence_values)
    plt.xlabel("Number of Topics")
    plt.ylabel("Coherence score")
    plt.legend(("coherence_values"), loc='best')
    plt.show()

#create corpus

def corpus(text):
  for j in range(1000):
    
    s='.'
    s=s.join(text)
    
  return s
